divs: Sighting Detailsgot up to go to bathroom looked out the window toward the east saw a very large object in the sky no sound big lights blueish white pulsating lights no plane lights on it no sound walked out on the porch took a very good look at it run back in and tried to find my cam it was gone when i went back out no sign of it call me i have more information to follow leading up to this night thank you i talked to the guy in fort worth texas about this he wanted me to put information here but i would like to talk to you if i can
